October 22, 2001

Notice #MS-91


NOTICE OF INTENTION TO TRANSFER


        Please be advised that effective with the close of business, October

19, 2001, the following member (s) have given notice of intention to

transfer their sole membership privileges:


Steven Thomas Schiff (TS-8132)


        Members and Member Firms have (10) days from the date of this notice

to advise the Corporate Secretary's Office of any claims in accordance with

Rule 2.51.


        Inquiries regarding the above should be addressed to the Member

Services Department at 212-299-2378.
